snippet.title: Flappy Eros - PlayStation 4 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Here's a rather strange one: what we have here is a Flappy Bird clone that originally came out on iOS in 2015 and it was ported to the PS4 in 2023, eight years after it was released. This one has no in-app purchases, which was a pretty wise move.

Developed by SilenGames
Also released on iOS
